title: 91: r/Choosingbeggars She STEALS Money from a Cancer Family!
description:
r/Choosingbeggars When a choosing beggar sees money, there's only one thing that goes through their mind: I DESERVE THAT MONEY! So when a choosing beggar sees somebody hand money to the family of a cancer victim, she does what comes naturally and grabs it right out of their hand. How incredibly shameless do you have to be to steal from actual cancer family? Some people are just disgusting!
